divs: Sighting Detailsat first one appeared and then two more about 20 min later. all three were blinking green, red, white, yellow, and orange lights randomly and they were also in a triangular formation east of Greenville, Texas. I have been watching for three hours now and they have not moved. at around 2AM three more objects appeared west of the first three also blinking the same color lights and also in a triangular formation.
Summary: witnessed 6 objects in the sky binking white green, red, yellow, and orange lights in a triangular formation for the last three hours. started around 1 AM east of Greenville, Texas.
